questiondata.strat-other: I tried to remember certain pairs of words, like mailman and package, or woman and lady. Others, I used from examples in my life. I heard Gedo (Japanese wrestler/booker for NJPW), but maybe it was Ghetto. Brand names (Xerox, Kleenex) were easier to remember than say, copier or tissue.
